Retis 1D example
================

Simulation
----------
task = retis
steps = 100
interfaces = [0.78, 0.80, 0.82, 0.84, 0.86, 0.87, 0.88, 0.90, 0.92, 0.95]

System
------
units = cp2k

Engine settings
---------------
class = cp2k
cp2k = /home/jonas/cp2k/exe/Linux-gnu-x86_64/cp2k.popt
input_path = cp2k_input
timestep = 0.5
subcycles = 1
cp2k_format = xyz
extra_files = ['BASIS_SET', 'GTH_POTENTIALS']

TIS settings
------------
freq = 0.5
maxlength = 20000
aimless = True
allowmaxlength = False
zero_momentum = False
rescale_energy = False
sigma_v = -1
seed = 0

RETIS settings
--------------
swapfreq = 0.5
relative_shoots = None
nullmoves = True
swapsimul = True

Initial-path
------------
method = kick
kick-from = previous

Orderparameter
--------------
class = MinDist
module = mindist.py
index = (0, 1)
periodic = True

Output
------
order-file = 1
restart-file = 1
trajectory-file = 10
